      "type": "text",
      "data": "\n\t\t\n\t\n\t\n\t\t<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 1\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: rgb(100.000000%, 100.000000%, 100.000000%)\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"column\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 22.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">  如何用半年的时间，从英语零基础到畅读原著\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">诺仔虽是</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">90</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">后，但</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">“</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">英语老师</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">的身份却已经伴随了本姑娘</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">年。从大学一年级起，无论是在国内还是在英国，都靠\n着教英语成功的养活了自己，欧耶!【你没看错，在一个英语为母语的国家，本姑娘也是个英语教书匠，哇哈!各\n位看官感兴趣的话，姑娘我会另起一篇分享下那段经历嗒!】\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">教过的学生众多，从小屁孩到国企老总，今天来跟大家谈谈让本诺印象最深亦是最骄傲的一个班。\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">时间</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">2015</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">年年底至</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">2016</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">年</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">7</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">月<br>\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">地点</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">:网络授课<br>\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">人物</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">:零基础成年人，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">30</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">岁</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">+\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">学英语原因:\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">1</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">、为小朋友:这一类基本都是妈妈，小朋友年龄都不大，为了能看懂小朋友的英文课本</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">&amp; </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">跟小家伙们一 起\n学，估摸着是让小</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">p</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">孩学的更有动力;\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">、旅游</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">&amp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">业务:这一类年龄稍微大一些，有的是自己创业，有时候需要与老外打交道，有的是退了休想出 国\n旅游，享受人生\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">共同特点</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">:几乎都是零基础，从</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">26</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">个字母学起!(一两人除外，有一点基础)\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">授课时间:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">每周</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">4</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">节课\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">课程安排:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">总的来说分为两部分，一:基础部分:音标</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">+</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">发音技巧。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">              二:场景部分:学情景对话，问路，电话，工作用语等\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">教了大半年的时间，看着从</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">ABC</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">开始学的他们后来可以过去式、现在时、将来时运用自如的写文章，甚至可以顺畅\n的读《阿拉丁神灯》等书虫读物，甚是为他们感到自豪啊!下面是诺老师总结的小白飞跃宝典，各位看官请参考:\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(46.666670%, 46.666670%, 46.666670%)\"> 一、基础很重要很重要很重要\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">其实大人学习跟小朋友会有通病，就是认为有些内容简单，或者认为某些内容看上去没有用，也就不认真学了。\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">最最最典型之一:语法\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">语法在大多数人看来是个无聊有烦人的小妖精，但诺仔却认为，语法君真的很可爱。必须得承认，刚开始接触的时\n候会觉得有些无聊</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">+</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">枯燥，只要踏实学一段时间，不用太长，一两个月就好，你便会发现它的可爱之处。至于学语\n法的小窍门，请参见:\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(0.000000%, 0.000000%, 93.333330%)\">简年</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(0.000000%, 0.000000%, 93.333330%)\">9: </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(0.000000%, 0.000000%, 93.333330%)\">老师一定没有告诉你，搞定</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(0.000000%, 0.000000%, 93.333330%)\">“</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(0.000000%, 0.000000%, 93.333330%)\">英语语法</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(0.000000%, 0.000000%, 93.333330%)\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(0.000000%, 0.000000%, 93.333330%)\">这个烦人的小妖精是有诀窍滴呀~\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">说回</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">wuli</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">学生。灰常显而易见的是，踏实学语法的童鞋，后来写文章、说英语时候都能非常准确的使用各种时态，\n并且表达的比不学语法的童鞋要地道的多的多的多。本来嘛，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">英语最重要的不是又音，而是英语思维!我们平日里\n所说的中式英语，绝大多数也是因为用中式思维在组词造句，与真正的英语相去甚远!\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"quiver-image-url/157407FE1CD3BCBA975B92211900B7D9.png\" alt=\"page1image6880\" width=\"429\" height=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"quiver-image-url/EFEE6A81F429CD7F65CC44ECB20F737D.png\" alt=\"page1image7040\" width=\"2\" height=\"15\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"quiver-image-url/9B681A1D996DA555473AA5001D7CCC5F.png\" alt=\"page1image7200\" width=\"280\" height=\"0\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 2\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: rgb(100.000000%, 100.000000%, 100.000000%)\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"column\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">最最最典型之二:音标\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"column\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">要说这音标的重要性啊，本诺认为语言已经没有办法描述它的重要了。有些发音是我们中文里没有的，那就更更更\n要提高警惕了，比如:不仅英语发音本身，包括听力啊，发音技巧(吞音、连读)之类的都跟它有着灰常重要的关\n系啊。倘若你认为自己的听力不好，可以想想看是不是音标就没学好，发音不准。长期发音不准的结果就是，听到\n正确的发音也不知道人家在说啥啦!\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">当然了，您要非得认为发音不标准没关系，反正老外也能听懂的。那本诺也没有办法，追求不一样嘛!本诺认为要\n学就要学标准，并且学的标准了再玩出花是很容易的，比如模仿各国又音这种东东就是本诺的心头大爱!啊哈!\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(46.666670%, 46.666670%, 46.666670%)\">二、每天听</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; font-weight: 700; color: rgb(46.666670%, 46.666670%, 46.666670%)\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(46.666670%, 46.666670%, 46.666670%)\">读，哪怕只是半小时\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">之前写过一篇\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(0.000000%, 0.000000%, 93.333330%)\">亲身经历告诉你，浸泡在英语环境里的总要性\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">不是要炫耀母上的开明啦，其实是想告诉大家就算我们没有生活在一个英文环境中，也要努力为自己创造一个出\n来，办法在原文里有，看官自行寻找</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">~</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">啊哈!\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">在小半年的教学中，诺老师不止一次的强调一定要泡在英语里，泡在英语里，泡在英语里，这个办法无论是对英语\n小白，还是大学霸，都是极好的!\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">哪怕每天只是半小时的读和听，只要是符合自身水平的，新概念也好，课文也好，演讲稿也好，不限内容，只要泡\n在里面半小时。这种效果是慢慢渗透出来进去，再慢慢显现出来的，在读和听的过程中，在你不知不觉中，很多英\n语语法、单词、语感就这样印在了脑中，随时准备备你调用!\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">哦对，忘记说，诺仔认为多听英文歌是很有好处的，前提是每一首歌做到精听，并且要选慢歌，比如《</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">heal the\nworld</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">》、《</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">how did I fall in love with you</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">》这一类的。一来慢歌歌词会唱的灰常清楚，二来每首歌都有它的韵\n脚，拿他来练习某个音标的发音甚是好玩</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">+</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">有效!\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(46.666670%, 46.666670%, 46.666670%)\">三、</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(46.666670%, 46.666670%, 46.666670%)\">一定要慢，慢，再慢<br>\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">记得有句话是这样说的:<br>\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">想要跳的高，先要蹲下来。\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">诺仔认为，想要英语学的好，先要慢下来。这里的慢，包括</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">慢慢学，慢慢读，慢慢说，慢慢品味。\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">慢慢学:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">是要你耐心大好基础，音标有</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">48</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">个，时态有</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">16</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">种，动词成千上万，针对不同时态又有着不同变化。这\n些，请你慢慢学。至少，在最初的最初，请慢，慢，再慢一点。请你相信，现在的慢，都是在为你以后起飞做准\n备。羽翼都没有长全的鹰，要怎么翱翔?\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">慢慢读:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">请先一个词一个词的读，再一个意相一个意相的读【拜托不要问我意相是什么，那样我还要再写一篇啊\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">~</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">】。一个词一个词是要你细细研究包括单复数，时态等等，意相是要你真的读明白某句话，本来嘛，人家英语就\n是靠意相来断句的嘛!\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">慢慢说</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">:是要你给自己一点思考的时间，用正确的英文思维来组句，而不是单纯的一个词一个词的中译英! 也是\n要你想清楚每句话的语法是否表达清楚，比如:是</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">Who cares</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">?不是</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">Who care</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">?更是要你养成边说边想的习惯，起\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"quiver-image-url/EFEE6A81F429CD7F65CC44ECB20F737D.png\" alt=\"page2image7680\" width=\"2\" height=\"15\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"quiver-image-url/167E12247AC2B0E3FEB8F00BE6688DE3.png\" alt=\"page2image7840\" width=\"160\" height=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"quiver-image-url/EFEE6A81F429CD7F65CC44ECB20F737D.png\" alt=\"page2image8000\" width=\"2\" height=\"15\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 3\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: rgb(100.000000%, 100.000000%, 100.000000%)\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"column\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<pre><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">初会需要反映一段时间，但后来完全是条件反射好嘛!\n</span></pre>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Bold'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">慢慢品味:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">是要你慢慢研究英语的每一种表达，单词发音、句子时态、习惯用语等等。会不会觉得，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">surprise</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">这个\n词发音对了，听上去就很惊喜?</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">deny </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">读起来就像有人在抵赖?</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">insanely</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">把不可思议表达到极值 (</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">insanely\nsmart</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">)?越是细细的品，越是觉得这语言实在太有意思!\n</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">作者:斯诺姑娘<br>\n链接:</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'Georgia'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">http://www.jianshu.com/p/075d1331bf07<br>\n</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.000000pt; font-family: 'STSongti-SC-Regular'; color: rgb(20.000000%, 20.000000%, 20.000000%)\">來源:简书\n著作权归作者所有。商业转载请联系作者获得授权，非商业转载请注明出处。&nbsp;</span></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>"
